<p class="p">Αφού έχετε <span class="link"><a href="bluetooth-connect-device.html.el" title="Συνδέστε τον υπολογιστή σας σε μια συσκευή Bluetooth">συνδεθεί σε μια συσκευή</a></span>, ούτε ο υπολογιστής σας ούτε η συσκευή δεν χρειάζεται να είναι ορατή για την μεταξύ τους επικοινωνία.</p>
<p class="p">Devices without a display usually have a pairing mode that can be entered
  by pressing a button, or a combination of buttons for a while, whether when
  they’ve already been turned on, or as they are being turned on.</p>
<p class="p">The best way to find out how to enter that mode is to refer to the device’s
  manual. For some devices, the procedure might be
  <span class="link"><a href="bluetooth-device-specific-pairing.html.el" title="Pairing instructions for specific devices">slightly different from usual</a></span>.
  </p>
